  "text": "The disturbance index was so far only tested for three boreal study regions dominated by coniferous species [CITATION_1] . Our study was the first to apply the disturbance index to temperate forest ecosystems with mainly broad-leaved and mixed forest types. Overall, the disturbance index performed very well and the accuracy assessment confirmed an accurate change map.",
